\begin_inset Formula $2\times2$
\end_inset

 matrices over the integers 
\begin_inset Formula $SL(2,\mathbb{Z})$
\end_inset

.
 Given that the Farey fraction is given by the ratio, so that 
\begin_inset Formula \[
\left(\begin{array}{cc}
-a & -b\\
-c & -d\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{cc}
a & b\\
c & d\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{cc}
-1 & 0\\
0 & -1\end{array}\right)\]

\end_inset

