\begin_layout Standard
An alternate labelling of an infinite binary tree is with the 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

dyadic rationals
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

, rational numbers of the form 
\begin_inset Formula $m/2^{n}$
\end_inset

