\begin_inset Formula \[
t_{w}\left(\frac{p}{2^{n}}\right)=w^{n-1}+\frac{1}{2}\left[t_{w}\left(\frac{p-1}{2^{n}}\right)+t_{w}\left(\frac{p+1}{2^{n}}\right)\right]\]

\end_inset

where we anchor the recurrence with 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{w}(0)=t_{w}(1)=0$
\end_inset

