\begin_inset Formula $H=-\log_{2}w$
\end_inset

 is called the Hurst parameter (need ref).
 The value 
\begin_inset Formula $w=1/4$
\end_inset

 is special, in that 
\begin_inset Formula $t_{1/4}(x)=4x(1-x)$
\end_inset

