\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

more or less
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 because some care has to be taken to define which bit expansion defines
 the derivative.
 In a certain sense, 
\begin_inset Formula $q_{\gamma}$
\end_inset

 is the dis-ambiguated derivative.
 This is left as an exercise.
 
