\begin_inset Formula $d_{0}=rd_{1}r$
\end_inset

, and so this family of left-right symmetric curves has a representation
 in terms of 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

.
