\alpha & \delta\\
\beta & \epsilon\end{array}\right)\;\textrm{ and }\;\left(\begin{array}{cc}
1-\alpha & \zeta\\
-\beta & \eta\end{array}\right)\]

\end_inset

 are less than one.
